2fd0c4623dae60036cd902e5082df5881b04d310.query: SELECT * FROM ( SELECT p.id, p.mod_venue_id, p.name, p.map_id, p.tags AS place_tags, lt.id AS place_location_type_id, lt.name AS category, pt.name AS position, ptt.name AS place_type, f.id AS floor_id, f.name AS floor, p.geo_lat, p.geo_long, p.geo_alt, p.scene_lat, p.scene_long, p.scene_alt, p.is_active, p.config, p.created_at, p.updated_at, p.sys_place_position_type_id FROM mod_place p LEFT OUTER JOIN sys_place_location_type lt ON p.sys_place_location_type_id = lt.id LEFT OUTER JOIN sys_place_position_type pt ON p.sys_place_position_type_id = pt.id LEFT OUTER JOIN sys_place_type ptt ON p.sys_place_type_id = ptt.id LEFT OUTER JOIN mod_floor f ON p.mod_floor_id = f.id WHERE p.sys_place_location_type_id IN (130) AND p.sys_place_position_type_id = 1 AND p.is_active = 1 AND p.mod_venue_id = :mod_venue_id UNION SELECT p.id, p.mod_venue_id, p.name, p.map_id, p.tags AS place_tags, lt.id AS place_location_type_id, lt.name AS category, pt.name AS position, ptt.name AS place_type, f.id AS floor_id, f.name AS floor, p.geo_lat, p.geo_long, p.geo_alt, p.scene_lat, p.scene_long, p.scene_alt, p.is_active, p.config, p.created_at, p.updated_at, p.sys_place_position_type_id FROM mod_place p LEFT OUTER JOIN sys_place_location_type lt ON p.sys_place_location_type_id = lt.id LEFT OUTER JOIN sys_place_position_type pt ON p.sys_place_position_type_id = pt.id LEFT OUTER JOIN sys_place_type ptt ON p.sys_place_type_id = ptt.id LEFT OUTER JOIN mod_floor f ON p.mod_floor_id = f.id WHERE p.sys_place_location_type_id IN (130) AND p.sys_place_position_type_id = 2 AND p.is_active = 1 AND p.mod_venue_id = :mod_venue_id ) ORDER BY name
